snippet.title: Sonic Robo-Blast! From The Past - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
go get it here:
https://halatnikov.github.io/

originally made for SRB2 Mod Direct, which you can check out here:
https://youtu.be/OQ7nw-RX2U8?t=662

Sonic Robo-Blast! From The Past is a remake of 2 classic fangames from 1998 on a new engine in "glorious standard definition 480p widescreen" with rad new features!
